  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  OSDI &gt; or equal 20 and eye lid inflammation , meibomian gland
             inflammation,conjunctival injection,follicle at tarsus , positive corneal staining ,
             tear break up time less than 8 seconds , tear volume less than 5.5 mm.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age below 18 yo

          -  Active infectious corneal disease

          -  Post penetrating keratoplasty or glaucoma drainage device

          -  Known allergy to medication

          -  Lactation , Pregnant
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
